law.text:
The Commission shall consider the following for each office in formulating its report and recommendations:
The scope of responsibilities of the office;
The education, skills, abilities, licensure, and certification required to perform the duties of the office;
The salaries of similar offices in other jurisdictions;
The time required to perform the duties of the office;
The salaries of subordinate employees under the direct supervision of the office;
The volume of workload of the office; and
Any other information that the Commission deems relevant.
